Base URL: <%= @base_url %>

Test Steps:
<% @test_steps.each_with_index do |step, index| %>
<%= index + 1 %>. <%= step %>
<% end %>

Expected Assertions:
<% @assertions.each do |assertion| %>
- <%= assertion %>
<% end %>

Use Playwright MCP tools to:
1. Execute each test step in sequence
2. Verify the assertions
3. Take screenshots for documentation
4. Report any failures or issues found
5. Provide a summary of the test results